I AM TWO! 🥳
Had a small celebration with my hoomans due to #covid19. Even though I can’t see my furriends, mum and dad made it up to me by giving me extra treats and new toys today! Hope that I can meet my dear friends again. Stay home and stay safe, everyone!! ❤️
